OL,3,CResidents near chemical factory told
OL,4,Cto wash and peel homegrown vegetables
OL,6,FAn investigation seen by ITV News
OL,7,Freveals how much of a cancer-causing
OL,8,Fchemical has been released from a
OL,9,Ffactory on the Lancashire coast, as
OL,10,Four Science Correspondent Martin Stew
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FA site of special scientific interest,
OL,14,Fthe River Wyre, flows into Morecambe
OL,15,FBay - but what flows into the river
OL,16,Fitself?
