OL,3,CResidents near chemical factory told
OL,4,Cto wash and peel homegrown vegetables
OL,6,FData shared with ITV News by Watershed
OL,7,FInvestigations shows that between 1950
OL,8,Fand 2012 nearly 115 tonnes of the
OL,9,Fchemicals were released into the
OL,10,Friver, nearby landfill and air.
OL,12,FEmissions have cut right back, but as
OL,13,Frecently as last year Leana Hosea from
OL,14,FWatershed Investigations still found
OL,15,Fsome leaching into the river.
