OL,3,CResidents near chemical factory told
OL,4,Cto wash and peel homegrown vegetables
OL,6,F"The highest level we found was 250
OL,7,Ftimes the legal level you're allowed
OL,8,Ffor drinking water. Obviously, you're
OL,9,Fnot drinking this but they're called
OL,10,Fforever chemicals for a reason because
OL,11,Fthey last for thousands of years.
OL,13,F"There's no suggestion that AGC the
OL,14,Fchemical company have done anything
OL,15,Fillegal they say they follow all
OL,16,Fenvironmental standards and argue that
OL,17,Fany new emissions are a result of
OL,18,Fhistorical contamination over a
OL,19,Fhundred years slowly working its way
OL,20,Finto the environment."
