OL,3,CResidents near chemical factory told
OL,4,Cto wash and peel homegrown vegetables
OL,6,FWyre Council is worried enough about
OL,7,Flevels of contamination in the soil -
OL,8,Fit's drafted in the environment agency
OL,9,Fto investigate potential health risks.
OL,10,FThey're also advising people to wash
OL,11,Fand peel vegetables grown in the
OL,12,Fnearby area.
OL,14,FProfessor Patrick Byrne is an expert
OL,15,Fin forever chemicals. He's been
OL,16,Fmonitoring the site.
OL,18,F"The actual long-term effects for
OL,19,Fhuman health and wildlife we just
OL,20,Fdon't know," he told me.
