OL,6,F"It's really hard to link
OL,7,Fcontamination and human health, that's
OL,8,Fwhat the investigation is for, but
OL,9,Fit's really difficult to link in an
OL,10,Farea like this in a local population
OL,11,Fthere's a lot of factors at play that
OL,12,Fdrive increases in the incidences of
OL,13,Fcancer."
OL,15,FOn Wednesday evening the council will
OL,16,Fhold the first of several public
OL,17,Fmeetings to address growing local
OL,18,Ffears.
